Designation: Java Developer 
Job Type: Permanent 
Exp: Fresher
Position: 8
Location: Vashi-Navi Mumbai (Trans-Harbour/Thane / Harbour)
Passout: Any
Percentage: Any
Qualification: B.E/B.Tech in IT / Computer Science or MCA
Salary: As per performance  
Bond: As per performance
Skills:  JAVA ****/ADVANCED**** JAVA / MYSQL/CSS/HTML/JQUERY/JAVASCRIPT
Preferred Skills: SPRINGBOOT / HIBERNATE 


NOTE:- 

1- Candidates must have completed a course in Java Technology
2- Salary will be upon the performance of every candidate.
**

**Skills &** **Responsibilities:
**
 You will be part of a talented team that is building mission critical enterprise grade applications.
 Participate in all phases of software development.
 Incumbent will be self-motivated and willing to learn and implement best practices.
 Understand functional and non-functional requirements and collaborate with stakeholders.
 A good understanding of OOP using Java programming is indispensable for this role.
 Develop, test, and maintain Java based applications.
 Document the code, create, and publish similar specs as applicable.
 Write Unit tests using JUnit or Cucumber-like standards as needed for the code.
 The role provides opportunity beyond Java server-side development.
 You will have opportunity to contribute towards frontend and other backend modules.
Must have:
 Good knowledge of Data Structure, Algorithm concepts, and OOP using Java.
 Basic understanding of: HTML and SQL.
Good to have:
 Project experience in Java technology.
